                                       Project: Wolfenstein Part III (The Agency )       You have now brutally beaten your way through the city in its most terrible post-apocalyptic state and you think you have found a safe haven but you have really walked into the creators of your nightmares trap, you have walked into The Agency.From the outside it looked like an alright place that you could shack up at for a few days but when you got inside and went to the bathroom you heard some screams through the vent and decided to see what was going on. You squeez your way into a vent to see whats going on and as you look you witness a large man in a blue suit shoot a young boy and  his mother, you now know there is something wrong and you try to escape quickly but in your attempt you are seen and some men are after you. You must escape. 